main event: Observers reported seeing several unidentified objects in the sky over Louisville, Kentucky during the period of October 22 to August 1966.
interesting points: The objects appeared to change directions, moving slowly and not at the speed of stars or planets., Red, green, and white flashing lights were observed., Observers used telescopes to view the objects carefully., The objects were possibly misidentified natural occurrences like satellites or planets., The sighting lasted for several hours.
